        ],
        [
          "The Lady in the Maze - An avatar of Lilith? A fae monster? A demon imprisoned in your soul? Who is she and why does she haunt you?"
        ],
        [
          "Alabastor - The leader of your pack. This Ventrue Antitribu keeps the pack under tight control"
        ],
        [
          "Felix - You have a strange connection with this Tzimisce and he seems to have genuine affection for you. You fear for him"
        ],
        [
          "Mr. Sticks- A former Paladin. Although Mr. Sticks is unaware of this, Felix and you destroyed his Inquistor in NY when he began to persecute those who followed the Path of Lillith."
        ],
